<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to CarRental</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #374151;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A11312, #8a0f0e);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .welcome-message {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .features {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .features h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .feature-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #6b7280;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        
        .feature-list li:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #A11312;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A11312, #8a0f0e);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #A11312;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">ðŸš— CarRental</div>
            <h1>Welcome to CarRental!</h1>
            <p>Your journey to convenient car rentals starts here</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-message">
                Hello <%= name %>! ðŸ‘‹
            </div>
            
            <div class="description">
                Thank you for joining CarRental! We're excited to have you as part of our community. 
                You now have access to a wide selection of vehicles for your rental needs.
            </div>
            
            <div class="features">
                <h3>What you can do now:</h3>
                <ul class="feature-list">
                    <li>Browse our extensive fleet of vehicles</li>
                    <li>Book cars for your trips and adventures</li>
                    <li>Manage your bookings and reservations</li>
                    <li>Read and write reviews for vehicles</li>
                    <li>Update your profile and preferences</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <a href="<%= loginUrl %>" class="cta-button">
                Start Exploring Vehicles
            </a>
            
            <div class="description">
                If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team. 
                We're here to help make your car rental experience smooth and enjoyable.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p><strong>The CarRental Team</strong></p>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="mailto:carrent@info.com">Email: carrent@info.com</a>
                <a href="tel:0768163367">Phone: 0768163367</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
                This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you didn't create an account, please ignore this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 